Signature Packaged Drinking Water’s Mangrove Replenishment Project is a step toward a greener, more resilient tomorrow. This initiative focuses on restoring vital ecosystems across five villages near Puri, Odisha.
Leading by example, celebrated stars from the Bengali film fraternity, influencers, and content creators came forward to pledge their support and stand for a better future.
